title: Redskins going crazy, Devin White interview (Football 4/25)
description:
Will Brinson, John Breech and Ryan Wilson break down the Redskins rumors of moving up in the draft, talk about Big Ben's extension, Justin Tucker's new contract, Kyler Murray skipping a charity appearance and Brinson's bird scooter incident. Then Brinson interviews LSU linebacker Devin White.
